434
00:47:58,910 --> 00:48:00,560
Pojedeme.

435
00:48:23,340 --> 00:48:25,050
<i>Bolelo to?</i>

436
00:48:25,050 --> 00:48:27,910
<i>Bolelo to?</i>

437
00:48:27,910 --> 00:48:30,480
<i>Plakala jste?</i>

438
00:48:34,190 --> 00:48:36,240
